Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:39.90,Main01,Gin,0,0,0,,Man! I can't take this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:42.66,Main01,Gin,0,0,0,,Damn it! Damn it! I demand a do over!
