Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.56,0:20:46.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった やったよ銀さん｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:44.59,Main01,Madao,0,0,0,,I did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:45.93,Main01,Madao,0,0,0,,I did it, Gin-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:53.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｵﾚ これで 脱ﾏﾀﾞｵｽﾊﾟｲﾗﾙ\Nこれで ﾏﾀﾞｵ卒業だ｡
