Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:30.30,Main01,N,0,0,0,,Justaway went outside the boundary at the fourth corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.92,0:21:31.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだって!?\Nｵﾚ よく聞こえなかったわ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.87,0:21:30.30,Main01,Madao,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that?
