Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,0:21:35.40,Main01,Madao,0,0,0,,My eyes are all teared up, so I can't see clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:38.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ってえことは…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:37.33,Main01,Gin,0,0,0,,Which means...
