Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:49.79,Main01,Gin,0,0,0,,Why me?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.19,0:21:52.42,Main01,Gin,0,0,0,,Hasegawa-san, what is this?!
